text: Göyazan Qazakh FK is an Azerbaijani football club. The club currently takes part in Azerbaijan First Division. ==History== The club was founded in 1978, re-established in 1986 and 2003. FC Goyazan participated in five Soviet Second League seasons during 1987–1991 years and ranked 5th in 1988 and made its best indicator. In 1986 they also won Azerbaijan USSR League. The team did not enter consecutively latest five Azerbaijan Cup seasons, even though it participated in Azerbaijan First Division. ==Achievements== *Azerbaijan USSR League Champions: 1 1986 ==League and domestic cup history== {|class="wikitable" |-bgcolor="#efefef" !
